ingle lasing mode regardless of the gain spectral\nbandwidth. This chip-scale semiconductor platform provides a unique route\ntowards fundamental explorations of PT physics and next generation of\noptoelectronic devices for optical communications and computing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 May 2014 18:15:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Oct 2014 03:00:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-21"}
