s favoring a quantum mechanism of signal propagation along a\nmicrotubule are provided. Overall we find that coherent energy transfer in\ntubulin and microtubules is biologically feasible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 May 2014 18:16:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-27"}
